The '''Haj family''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] family that owned [[Haj Shipping Lines]]. They chose to not pick sides during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], but rather to serve both the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] and the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebellion]].

